ZH: 从不放弃，你会看到成功的那一天。
EN: Never give up, and you will see the day of success.
ZH: 从不认输，我会为自己的梦想努力。
EN: I never give up, I will work hard for my dreams.
ZH: 从不轻易改变计划，我会坚持原则。
EN: I never change plans easily, I will stick to my principles.
ZH: 从不逃避困难，我会积极应对。
EN: I never escape from difficulties, I will actively face them.
ZH: 从不说谎，诚实是我的底线。
EN: I never lie, honesty is my bottom line.
ZH: 从不迟到，守时是我的习惯。
EN: I never arrive late, punctuality is my habit.
ZH: 从不抱怨，我选择积极面对生活。
EN: I never complain, I choose to face life positively.
ZH: 从不伤害他人，我尊重每一个人。
EN: I never hurt others, I respect everyone.
ZH: 从不放纵自己，自律是我的原则。
EN: I never indulge myself, self-discipline is my principle.
ZH: 从不浪费时间，珍惜每一刻。
EN: I never waste time, cherish every moment.
ZH: 从不忘记家人，他们是我生命中的支柱。
EN: I never forget my family, they are the foundation of my life.
ZH: 从不停止学习，知识是无止境的。
EN: I never stop learning, knowledge has no bounds.
ZH: 从不对别人说谎，诚实是最重要的。
EN: I never lie to others, honesty is the most important.
ZH: 从不推卸责任，做事要有担当。
EN: I never shirk responsibility, one must take responsibility for their actions.
ZH: 从不沉溺于失败，我会坚强面对挑战。
EN: I never wallow in failure, I will face challenges with strength.
ZH: 从不退缩，困难只能让我更坚强。
EN: I never retreat, difficulties only make me stronger.
ZH: 从不懈怠，追求进步是我的信念。
EN: I never slack off, pursuing progress is my belief.
ZH: 从不停止奔跑，只求让自己更好。
EN: I never stop running, only to make myself better.
ZH: 从不放弃努力，成功总会属于坚持的人。
EN: I never give up effort, success will always belong to those who persevere.
